guest_message: Hey there! I'd like to order a BBQ Bacon Burger, please. Can you make it medium well and with onion rings on the side? Thanks!

Sure thing, you can put it under Thomas Wright. Thanks for confirming the order details and the parking space info. Looking forward to picking it up soon!
